{
  "stem": "26142.16",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said macaroni with marmalade, we are going to get tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the room, in this block, was already a Christmas tree was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what time we have to get up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and-- and by that time, we were given-- we were given aluminum-- aluminum-- it's [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] what they had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You could use it for coffee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You could use it for-- for-- for soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It had a-- a holder, that what we were given out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was our first day in-- in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Next day-- next day, we that-- that-- we that came, the new ones, were up to get our coffee.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Breakfast was-- that wasn't coffee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was ersatz cafe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it was black, but it was hot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we were not to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were not to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But the old ones that were in this-- in this block, they would go to their regular.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they went out to work and we-- a group came in and started registering everyone and asking them-- asking everyone if they had some kind of a trade.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and I remember that I-- I registered that I'm-- I'm a carpenter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I understand carpentry because I figured this is close.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My parents were in the lumber business and it might be better than saying that you have no trade, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anyway, and then we went-- we went through that selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The selection was a doctor that was standing on a-- on a pedestal and he was just piercing everybody with his eyes, looking over.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
